      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\">A patient presented with a sudden decrease in vision in right eye. While assessing his pupils, when light was shone in the left eye, both pupils constricted and when light was shone in the right eye, both pupils dilated. The likely abnormality is:</span></p>",
